Object

Type Parameters:
S - generator-type

All Implemented Interfaces:
Generator<T>, TransformingGenerator<T,S>, ElementWriter<T>
public class SingleFileTypeGeneratorBridge<S,T,V> extends SingleFileTypeGenerator<T,S>
Allows us to call an SingleFileTypeGenerator<V,S> as if it was an SingleFileTypeGenerator<T,S> using an function to connect the two.
Author:
Owen Feehan
